&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Second, what type of poison were you using?&amp;nbsp; Was it an old school poison, or one from the PoP era that added a buff to you?&amp;nbsp; If it was an old school poison, the poison works on the very first attack with the weapon, and is then gone.&amp;nbsp; If it was one of the PoP-era ones, then the proc *should* be independant of the weapon proc level/proc rate.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
